- Net result: Given equal value on headroom, drums, guitar attack, and vocal placement, CD 1 satisfies all four; CD 2 compromises two of them (attack and vocal immediacy). Therefore the Immediate 17-11-70 live set is the better match for my documented preferences and avoids the exact processing choices I explicitly dislike.

